Subject: Shadel Bandit Ring <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Hi,<br>
<br>
First I'd really like to say thank you for the focus items, I think theyare wonderful. Thanks also for converting the Testament of Vanear effect to something people who do the quest can use (Mana Preservation I).<br>
<br>
However, I think an error has been made when you changed the effect on theShadel Bandit Ring. It isn't at all easy for chars below 50 to go get one of these in Fungus Grove, and I think that the Extended Enhancement III effect that was on the ring was a fitting effect for the item. You changed<br>
this to Summoning Haste II. This has to be an error. This ring is All/All, and while many classes can cast buffs, fewer cast summoning spells. I'd like to plead with you to please, please give this item Extended Enhancement III once more. This one change has sucked most of the joy I<br>
had from the focus items out of me.<br>
<br>
Thanks also for Surefall druid newbie quests.<br>
 <p><img src=http://www.auburn.edu/~priceke/bobosig1.jpg width=320 height=180><br>
Bobolink Wareagle
